      • getInitialPropertyTransformers

        public Mapping<N,​T> getInitialPropertyTransformers​(TransformerSerializer<T,​L,​AP> serializer)
        Returns a Mapping which maps nodes to their initial property transformer. This method requires a TransformerSerializer as all property transform are stored as Strings in this class. The returned map is not cached and will be re-computed on each call.
        Parameters:
        serializer - used to deserialize each property transformer from a String.
        Returns:
        a Mapping which maps nodes to their initial property transformer
